[Metal creaking]

23:37.764 --> 23:40.331
[Siren sounds weakly]

23:44.335 --> 23:49.906
[Siren blaring]

23:49.950 --> 23:58.219
♪♪

23:58.262 --> 24:00.787
Here we go.

24:00.830 --> 24:10.492
♪♪

24:10.536 --> 24:16.237
♪♪

24:20.676 --> 24:22.591
[Siren blaring]

24:22.635 --> 24:27.509
[Walkers growling]

24:27.553 --> 24:31.078
[Grunting]

24:33.384 --> 24:41.741
♪♪

24:41.784 --> 24:44.744
[Walkers growling]

24:44.787 --> 24:51.490
♪♪

24:51.533 --> 24:54.188
Come on! Keep up!

24:54.231 --> 24:59.280
[Grunting]

24:59.323 --> 25:03.850
[Siren stops]

25:03.893 --> 25:07.549
♪♪

25:07.593 --> 25:10.552
[Walkers growling]

25:10.596 --> 25:13.294
♪♪

25:13.337 --> 25:15.949
[Grunts]

25:15.992 --> 25:20.693
[Walkers growling]

25:20.736 --> 25:30.703
♪♪

25:30.746 --> 25:39.712
♪♪

25:39.755 --> 25:43.193
♪♪

25:43.237 --> 25:46.370
Iris:
"Tyger Tyger, burning bright,

25:46.414 --> 25:48.721
in the forests of the night;

25:48.764 --> 25:50.723
what immortal hand or eye,

25:50.766 --> 25:54.030
could frame
thy fearful symmetry?"

25:54.074 --> 25:55.771
[Breathing heavily]

25:55.815 --> 26:04.650
♪♪

26:04.693 --> 26:09.916
"In what distant deeps or skies

26:09.959 --> 26:12.266
burnt the fire of thine eyes?"

26:12.309 --> 26:13.746
[Lighter clicks]

26:13.789 --> 26:19.142
♪♪

26:19.186 --> 26:22.798
"On what wings dare he aspire?"

26:22.842 --> 26:26.149
♪♪

26:26.193 --> 26:29.196
"What the hand,
dare seize the fire?"

26:29.239 --> 26:39.206
♪♪

26:39.249 --> 26:49.216
♪♪

26:49.259 --> 26:50.696
♪♪

26:50.739 --> 26:53.133
"And what shoulder and what art

26:53.176 --> 26:56.179
could twist the sinews
of thy heart?

26:56.223 --> 26:59.052
And when thy heart
began to beat,

26:59.095 --> 27:03.709
what dread hand
and what dread feet?

27:03.752 --> 27:07.713
What the hammer?
What the chain?

27:07.756 --> 27:10.846
In what furnace was thy brain?

27:10.890 --> 27:12.674
What the anvil?

27:12.718 --> 27:18.680
What dread grasp,  dare its deadly terrors clasp!"

27:18.724 --> 27:21.117
[Walkers growling]Aah!

27:21.161 --> 27:22.423
♪♪

27:22.466 --> 27:25.861
[Grunts]

27:25.905 --> 27:28.385
♪♪

27:28.429 --> 27:29.648
Aah! Aah!

27:29.691 --> 27:33.521
[Growling continues]

27:33.564 --> 27:35.958
♪♪

27:36.002 --> 27:39.309
Aah!

27:39.353 --> 27:43.009
[Ears ringing]

27:43.052 --> 27:44.445
[Groans]

27:44.488 --> 27:48.101
[Growling continues]

27:48.144 --> 27:58.024
♪♪

27:58.067 --> 28:07.686
♪♪

28:07.729 --> 28:17.173
♪♪

28:17.217 --> 28:18.697
♪♪

28:18.740 --> 28:21.569
[Growling]

28:21.612 --> 28:31.231
♪♪

28:31.274 --> 28:40.980
♪♪

28:41.023 --> 28:47.900
♪♪

28:47.943 --> 28:51.860
"When the stars
threw down their spears

28:51.904 --> 28:54.994
and water'd heaven
with their tears..."

28:55.037 --> 29:04.786
♪♪

29:04.830 --> 29:09.965
♪♪

29:10.009 --> 29:13.360
"...did He smile His work
to see?"

29:13.403 --> 29:15.971
Monument High is a great,
great way

29:16.015 --> 29:17.364
to meet people
your age.

29:17.407 --> 29:24.066
♪♪

29:24.110 --> 29:25.851
This is
your new home now.

29:25.894 --> 29:27.461
You get
a fresh start.

29:27.504 --> 29:30.159
Iris:
Ha ha! Yeah!

29:30.203 --> 29:31.726
[Laughter]

29:31.770 --> 29:35.034
"Did He who made the Lamb
make thee?"

29:35.077 --> 29:36.731
♪♪

29:36.775 --> 29:38.385
[Walker growling][Grunts]

29:38.428 --> 29:44.130
♪♪

29:44.173 --> 29:46.001
Get them out!
I got it!

29:46.045 --> 29:47.916
Come on!

29:47.960 --> 29:49.570
Aah!

29:49.613 --> 29:50.919
[Grunting]

29:50.963 --> 29:52.312
♪♪

29:52.355 --> 29:54.270
Aah!

29:54.314 --> 29:56.055
♪♪

29:56.098 --> 29:58.318
Oh, wait!
I need my bag!
Elton!

29:58.361 --> 29:59.667
♪♪

29:59.710 --> 30:03.018
[Grunting]

30:03.062 --> 30:05.238
♪♪

30:05.281 --> 30:08.154
[Walkers growling]

30:08.197 --> 30:18.164
♪♪

30:18.207 --> 30:21.602
♪♪

30:21.645 --> 30:24.692
"Tyger Tyger, burning bright,

30:24.735 --> 30:27.826
in the forests of the night;

30:27.869 --> 30:30.785
what immortal hand or eye,

30:30.829 --> 30:34.833
dare frame
thy fearful symmetry?"

30:34.876 --> 30:36.835
♪♪

30:36.878 --> 30:39.011
[Growling continues]

